<h4><%= event.name %></h4>

<p><%= event.desc %></p>
<p><%= event.date %></p>

<br><h5>create an "ask" for your event</h5>
<p>If there's two big trees invariably sooner or later there's gonna be a little tree. I thought today we would do a happy little picture. Let's do it again then, what the heck. By now you should be quite happy about what's happening here.</p>

<div>
	<form method="PUT" action="/events/event-setup">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s6 input-field">
				<label>event name</label>
				<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="your event name" >
			</div>
			<div class="col s3 input-field">
				<label>date of event (optional)</label>
				<input type="date" name="date" placeholder="date of event">
			</div>
		</div> 
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col s9 input-field">
				<label>event decription</label>
				<input type="text" name="desc" placeholder="describe your event">
			</div>
		</div>

		<input type="hidden" name="userId" value=req.body.id>

		<button class="waves-effect waves-light btn" type="submit" name="action">start your event!<i class="material-icons right">add</i>
		</button>
	</form>
	
</div>






